==English==

===Etymology===
* {{compound|freedom|of|speech}}

===Pronunciation===
{{rfp|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# The [[right]] of [[citizen]]s of the [[United States]] to [[speak]], or otherwise [[communicate]], without fear of harm or [[prosecution]].

====Related terms====
* [[free speech]]

====Coordinate terms====
* [[freedom of movement]], [[freedom of contract]], [[freedom of the press]], [[freedom of religion]], [[freedom of assembly]], [[right to petition]], [[right to keep and bear arms]]

